OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FThe US military have reimposed a
OL,7,Fblockade on Iranian ports, following
OL,8,FTehran's attacks on ships trying to
OL,9,Fpass through the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,11,FResponding to the blockade, Iran's
OL,12,Fparamilitary Revolutionary Guard
OL,13,Fthreatened to halt all energy exports
OL,14,Ffrom the Middle East.
OL,16,F"The export of oil and gas from the
OL,17,Fregion will be either for everyone or
OL,18,Ffor no one," it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
