FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FAnother wave of US strikes on Iran,
OL,7,Fand Iranian attacks on shipping and US
OL,8,Fallies, have again threatened the
OL,9,Fprogress of an agreement to open the
OL,10,Fstrait, which is a key waterway to the
OL,11,Fworld's energy supplies.
OL,13,FThe first blockade was imposed by the
OL,14,FUS in mid-April, and then lifted it in
OL,15,Fmid-June, a day after signing the
OL,16,Finterim deal that set a 60-day period
OL,17,Ffor negotiations over issues like
OL,18,FIran's nuclear program.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FHowever, talks have stalled as
OL,7,Ffighting over the strait has
OL,8,Fintensified.
OL,10,FWhen US President Donald Trump
OL,11,Fannounced the return of the blockade
OL,12,Fon Monday, he also said he would
OL,13,Fimpose a 20% fee on ships passing
OL,14,Fthrough the strait.
OL,16,FHowever, he dropped the plan to
OL,17,Fcollect fees hours before resuming the
OL,18,Fblockade, citing requests from allies
OL,19,Fin the Persian Gulf.
OL,21,FBoth the US and Iran launch attacks
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FThe US carried out another wave of
OL,7,Fstrikes as it reimposed the blockade,
OL,8,Fstriking dozens of targets over seven
OL,9,Fhours, the US military's Central
OL,10,FCommand said on Wednesday.
OL,12,FMissile alert warnings went out in
OL,13,FBahrain and Kuwait early Wednesday
OL,14,Fmorning as they faced incoming Iranian
OL,15,Ffire. This has been a daily
OL,16,Foccurrence, further straining a
OL,17,Fceasefire in the war.
OL,19,FJordan also said it shot down three
OL,20,Fincoming Iranian missiles. Iran
OL,21,Fclaimed attacks on the three nations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FUS Navy Adm. Brad Cooper, who leads
OL,7,FCentral Command, said in a statement
OL,8,Fthat Iran had launched dozens of
OL,9,Fmissiles and drones at neighboring
OL,10,FGulf Arab countries.
OL,12,F"US forces are holding Iran
OL,13,Faccountable for unwarranted aggression
OL,14,Fthat continues to endanger innocent
OL,15,Flives," Cooper said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
