OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FThere are currently at least 19 US
OL,7,Fwarships in the Arabian Sea, and
OL,8,FCentral Command said in a social media
OL,9,Fpost that there are "hundreds of
OL,10,Fmilitary aircraft operating across the
OL,11,FMiddle East."
OL,13,FWhen the US and Israel launched the
OL,14,Fwar on Iran on 28 February, Tehran
OL,15,Feffectively shut the Strait of Hormuz
OL,16,Fby attacking and threatening ships.
OL,17,FThat sent the price of oil, fertilizer
OL,18,Fand other goods soaring globally.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
