OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FIran has more recently attacked ships
OL,7,Fmoving through the strait on a route
OL,8,Fnear Oman overseen by the US military
OL,9,Fthat is outside Tehran's control,
OL,10,Fsetting off the recent violence.
OL,12,FThe US has threatened to reopen the
OL,13,Fstrait by force ` but experts say that
OL,14,Fwould require a much bigger armada if
OL,15,Fnot tens of thousands of ground troops.
OL,17,FIran's ambassador to the United
OL,18,FNations, Amir Saeid Iravani,
OL,19,Fcriticised America's ongoing attacks
OL,20,Ftargeting his country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
