PN,31808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FTrump told Fox News Channel on Tuesday
OL,7,Fnight that more US strikes against
OL,8,FIran were coming over the next two
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,F"You better make a deal, or you're not
OL,12,Fgoing to have anything left," Trump
OL,13,Fwarned.
OL,15,FSubscribe for to our weekly newsletter
OL,16,Ffor exclusive and original coverage
OL,17,Ffrom ITV News. Direct to your inbox
OL,18,Fevery Friday morning.
OL,20,FInterim deal hangs in the balance
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
