CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FUnder the interim deal, Iran agreed
OL,7,Fthat passage through the strait would
OL,8,Fremain free of charge for 60 days `
OL,9,Fbut the agreement left open what would
OL,10,Fhappen after. Iran asserts it has the
OL,11,Fright to manage traffic and
OL,12,Fpotentially charge fees. The US has
OL,13,Fdisputed that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,319,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1784168292
OL,3,CTehran threatens to halt energy
OL,4,Cexports after US reimposes its blockade
OL,6,FThe price for a barrel of Brent crude
OL,7,Foil, the international standard,
OL,8,Fbriefly topped $87 (#64.86) early on
OL,9,FTuesday, still well below the nearly
OL,10,F$120 reached at the height of the war.
OL,11,FThe price dipped to $78 (58.15) in the
OL,12,Faftermath of Trump's announcement that
OL,13,Fhe had changed course.
OL,15,FRegional mediators meanwhile are still
OL,16,Ftrying to get the United States and
OL,17,FIran back to the negotiating table.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
